<h1 class="gdl-page-title gdl-title title-color">Emergencies and Closures</h1>
<div class="gdl-page-caption gdl-divider"></div>
</div>
<div class="gdl-page-float-left"><div class="gdl-page-item"><div class="sixteen columns mb20"><div class="gdl-page-content">
<p><strong><em>Emergency closures cover not only snow days, but any unforeseen incident in which school must be closed.  Announcements of such closures will be made via: </em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><em>FBCS texting service</em></strong></li>
<li><em>Social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, Twitter) </em></li>
<li><em>Canvas </em></li>
<li><em>www.forrestbirdcharterschool.org</em></li>
<li><em>KPND and KPBX radio stations </em></li>
<li><em>KREM and KHQ television stations</em></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><em>If LPOSD is closed for snow, FBCS will be as well.  If Bonners Ferry schools are closed, FBCS will be open but we will not run the North Bus. </em></strong></p>
<p><strong><em>At times there may be a need to close the school early due to weather.  We will send this information out via texting, Canvas, social media and the website.  </em></strong></p>
</div></div></div></div>		
						
